Saigon male (MNHN). 345 habitus dorsal; 346 habitus ventral; 347, 348 terminal abdomen: 347 ventral; 348 dorsal; 349, 350 dissected terminal abdomen after soaking in soapy water for an hour: 349 ventral (base of lateral hooks on ML arrowed); 350 left lateral (hooks arising from ML arrowed); 351−353 aedeagal sheath: 351 left lateral; 352 ventral; 353 dorsal; 354, 355 aedeagus: 354 ventral; 355 right lateral.
